ite\":0,\"totalTokens\":22809,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1772443348234}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"3387a909\",\"parentId\":\"f0a4e8a7\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-02T09:28:16.497Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"[Mon 2026-03-02 17:28 GMT+8] 调用memory search mcp把今天的记忆都向量化一下\"}],\"timestamp\":1772443696494}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"662d8699\",\"parentId\":\"3387a909\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-02T09:28:30.574Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"用户要我把今天的记忆向量化，这是要用 memory search MCP 工具。根据 TOOLS.md，我应该用 `memory_search` 工具。\\n\\n不过等一下，`memory_search` 工具是用于搜索的，不是用于向量化记忆的。我需要检查一下 memory-search 这个 SKILL.md，看看有没有向量化的功能。\\n\\n根据技能列表，有一个 `memory-search` 技能：\\n```\\n<skill>\\n  <name>memory-search</name>\\n  <description>Semantic memory search with vector + BM25 hybrid retrieval via MCP. Use when you need to search past memories, find relevant context from episodic/semantic/procedural memory, recall what happened on a date, or retrieve knowledge that was previously stored. Also use when memory_search, memory_get, memory_sync, or memory_status tools are needed.</description>\\n  <location>D:\\\\.openclaw\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\skills\\\\memory-search\\\\SKILL.md</location>\\n</skill>\\n```\\n\\n这个技能描述说\\\"Use when you need to search past memories\\\"，但没有明确说可以用来向量化记忆。\\n\\n让我看看系统中可用的工具。`memory_search` 工具的描述是：\\n```\\n\\\"Mandatory recall step: semantically search MEMORY.md + memory/*.md (and optional session transcripts) before answering questions about prior work, decisions, dates, people, preferences, or todos; returns top snippets with path + lines.\\\"\\n\\n如果 response has disabled=true, memory retrieval is unavailable and should be surfaced to the user.\\\"\\n```\\n\\n这个工具是搜索用的，不是用来向量化存储的。用户的请求可能不太对。我应该先读一下 memory-search 的 SKILL.md，看看有没有向量化记忆的功能。\\n\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"tool-523212aec34a4a2ba9638c0750b2b580\",\"name\":\"read\",\"arguments\":{\"file_path\":\"D:\\\\.openclaw\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\skills\\\\memory-search\\\\SKILL.md\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"bailian\",\"model\":\"glm-4.7\",\"usage\":{\"input\":17248,\"output\":739,\"cacheRead\":5119,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":23106,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1772443696496}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"87e1dcec\",\"parentId\":\"662d8699\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-02T09:28:30.584Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"toolResult\",\"toolCallId\":\"tool-523212aec34a4a2ba9638c0750b2b580\",\"toolName\":\"read\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"---\\nname: memory-search\\ndescription: Semantic memory search with vector + BM25 hybrid retrieval via MCP. Use when you need to search past memories, find relevant context from episodic/semantic/procedural memory, recall what happened on a date, or retrieve knowledge that was previously stored. Also use when memory_search, memory_get, memory_sync, or memory_status tools are needed.\\nmetadata:\\n  {\\n    \\\"openclaw\\\":\\n      {\\n        \\\"emoji\\\": \\\"🧠\\\",\\n        \\\"requires\\\": { \\\"bins\\\": [\\\"python\\\", \\\"mcporter\\\"] },\\n      },\\n  }\\n---\\n\\n# Memory Search（记忆语义搜索）\\n\\n基于 **向量余弦相似度 + BM25 关键词** 的混合搜索系统。将 workspace 下的记忆文件（MEMORY.md、RECENT_MEMORY.md、memory/**/*.md）自动分块、生成 embedding、存入 SQLite，提供高质量语义检索。\\n\\n## 架构\\n\\n```\\n记忆文件 (.md)\\n    ↓ chunk_markdown (tiktoken, 400 tokens, 80 overlap)\\n    ↓ embed (DashScope text-embedding-v3 / OpenAI)\\n    ↓ SQLite (chunks + FTS5)\\n    ↓\\n搜索：向量相似度 × 0.7 + BM25 × 0.3 → 排序 → 过滤 (min_score 0.35)\\n```\\n\\n## MCP 工具\\n\\n通过 `mcporter call memory_search.<tool>` 调用：\\n\\n### memory_search\\n\\n语义搜索记忆。\\n\\n```bash\\nmcporter call memory_search.memory_search query=\\\"用户的偏好设置\\\"\\nmcporter call memory_search.memory_search query=\\\"上周做了什么\\\" max_results=10\\n```\\n\\n### memory_get\\n\\n读取具体记忆文件。\\n\\n```bash\\nmcporter call memory_search.memory_get path=\\\"memory/episodic/2026-03-01.md\\\"\\nmcporter call memory_search.memory_get path=\\\"MEMORY.md\\\" start_line=0 lines=50\\n```\\n\\n### memory_sync\\n\\n手动触发索引同步（扫描文件变更，重新分块+embedding）。\\n\\n```bash\\nmcporter call memory_search.memory_sync\\n```\\n\\n### memory_status\\n\\n查看索引状态。\\n\\n```bash\\nmcporter call memory_search.memory_status\\n```\\n\\n## 使用场景\\n\\n1. **自动上下文注入**：对话开始时搜索相关记忆，注入系统提示\\n2. **精确回忆**：用户问\\\"我之前说过什么关于…\\\"时搜索\\n3. **知识检索**：从 semantic memory 中查找事实和概念\\n4. **时间线回溯**：从 episodic memory 中查找特定日期的事件\\n\\n## 注意事项\\n\\n- MCP 服务器启动时会自动同步一次索引\\n- 文件未变更（hash 相同）时跳过，不会重复消耗 embedding 配额\\n- 默认使用 DashScope text-embedding-v3（1024 维），也支持 OpenAI\\n- 搜索结果包含 score，0.35 以下自动过滤\\n- SQLite 数据库在 `D:\\\\.openclaw\\\\.openclaw\\\\memory\\\\search_index.sqlite`\\n\"}],\"isError\":false,\"timestamp\":1772443710580}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"8fd2abc4\",\"parentId\":\"87e1dcec\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-02T09:28:54.191Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"用户要我调用 memory search MCP 把今天的记忆都向量化一下。根据 SKILL.md，我需要用 `mcporter call memory_search.memory_sync` 来触发索引同步，扫描文件变更，重新分块+embedding。\\n\\n按照 TOOLS.md 的说明，我必须在 workspace 目录（`D:\\\\.openclaw\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace`）下执行，用 `npx mcporter call`。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"tool-2faa119b832a472b9e155ad4da4107c6\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"cd D:\\\\.openclaw\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace && npx mcporter call memory_search.memory_sync\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"bailian\",\"model\":\"glm-4.7\",\"usage\":{\"input\":22384,\"output\":203,\"cacheRead\":639,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":23226,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":177