{"type":"message","id":"178f7512","parentId":"fc14ab44","timestamp":"2026-03-02T12:57:03.620Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5bd45a4fbc3049ae93344120","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"86cb6660\",\"parentId\":\"602d34af\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-02T09:59:11.006Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"我传参数的格式有问题。让我看一下正确格式。根据工具定义，request 应该是一个对象，包含 kind 和其他字段。\\n\\n让我重新调用：\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"tool-cd0c217e8e474ff59bcab5a7a5220876\",\"name\":\"browser\",\"arguments\":{\"action\":\"act\",\"ref\":\"e229\",\"request\":{\"fn\":\"e229.click(); e229.focus(); e229.value = '被夺舍3次后我发现自己连不都不会说'; e229.dispatchEvent(new Event('input', { bubbles: true })); return e229.value;\",\"kind\":\"evaluate\"},\"targetId\":\"08B482389D09F7C5B0E1240E1425BE0F\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"bailian\",\"model\":\"glm-4.7\",\"usage\":{\"input\":1457,\"output\":177,\"cacheRead\":82111,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":83745,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1772445545476}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"5129f700\",\"parentId\":\"86cb6660\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-02T09:59:11.058Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"toolResult\",\"toolCallId\":\"tool-cd0c217e8e474ff59bcab5a7a5220876\",\"toolName\":\"browser\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"{\\n  \\\"status\\\": \\\"error\\\",\\n  \\\"tool\\\": \\\"browser\\\",\\n  \\\"error\\\": \\\"Can't reach the OpenClaw browser control service. Restart the OpenClaw gateway (OpenClaw.app menubar, or `openclaw gateway`). Do NOT retry the browser tool — it will keep failing. Use an alternative approach or inform the user that the browser is currently unavailable. (Error: Error: page.evaluate: Error: Invalid evaluate function: Unexpected token ';'\\\\n    at anonymous (eval at evalu