{"type":"message","id":"e5caf165","parentId":"a34d4bcd","timestamp":"2026-03-02T15:01:04.984Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问为什么只索引了 11 个文件，我需要统计一下符合扫描规则的文件数量，然后解释 memory-search-mcp 的扫描逻辑。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"算一下：\n- `MEMORY.md` ✅\n- `RECENT_MEMORY.md` ✅\n- `memory/**/*.md` = 10 个\n\n总共 12 个，但失败了 1 个（MEMORY.md，batch size 问题），所以索引了 11 个。\n\n**其他文件（AGENTS.md, SOUL.md, TOOLS.md, USER.md, HEARTBEAT.md, IDENTITY.md, dashboard.md）不会被索引**，因为 memory-search-mcp 只扫描 `MEMORY.md`、`RECENT_MEMORY.md` 和 `memory/` 目录。\n\n你要想索引其他文件，得改 `mcp_memory_server.py` 的扫描逻辑，或者把那些文件移到 `memory/` 目录下。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":255903,"output":233,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":256136,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772463660643}}
